title: 'Basically what I needed'

title: 'Useless'

title: 'I wish I could get my refund!!'
body: 'These are really thin in diameter  Really wish if they could have given better ones! I missed this item at my place post delivery and just today saw the quality stick with them as I can’t return them'

title: 'Not water absorbent.'
body: 'Though the product is of cork material
column5: it does not absorb water. It is okey to keep hot cups etc but not suitable for glasses with ice.'

title: 'Decent product'
body: 'I bought it to use as base for small indoor planters and it serves the purpose well. But at 350 for 10 I feel it is bit overpriced considering it is thin and is not hard or strong.'

title: 'Good product'
body: 'I liked it. And a good product. Worth the money.'

title: 'Fantastic'
body: 'Best deal to start your coaster collection.'
